# Everything else keeps connect-src TIGHT (no external origins: 'self' + blob: + nano-gpt.com only;
# blob: is local, see note above). play.html runs UNTRUSTED shared apps (arbitrary bundled
# HTML/JS): the tight external gate stops a malicious app from fetch-exfiltrating the viewer's
# inputs or API key to an attacker origin. legal.html is plain content but defaults to the same
# tight policy.
#
# EXCEPTION — /play + /play.html add two URL-shortener origins (tinyurl.com, da.gd) to
# connect-src, and ONLY connect-src (never img/media/script/frame). These are for the TRUSTED
# parent chrome's opt-in "shorten this share link" button. The UNTRUSTED shared app does NOT get
# them: it runs in a srcdoc iframe that re-seals its OWN connect-src back to 'self' blob: nano-gpt
# via a <meta> CSP (PREVIEW_CSP in play.html), and the browser enforces every delivered policy by
# intersection — so a malicious app still cannot reach the shorteners to exfiltrate viewer
# inputs/outputs. Exact 3-host list, never a wildcard. legal.html stays fully tight.
/play
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; img-src 'self' data: blob: https://nano-gpt.com; media-src 'self' data: blob: https:; connect-src 'self' blob: https://nano-gpt.com https://tinyurl.com https://da.gd; frame-src 'self' blob:; child-src blob:; worker-src 'self' blob:; font-src 'self' data:; base-uri 'none'; form-action 'none'; object-src 'none'; frame-ancestors 'self'; upgrade-insecure-requests
/play.html
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; img-src 'self' data: blob: https://nano-gpt.com; media-src 'self' data: blob: https:; connect-src 'self' blob: https://nano-gpt.com https://tinyurl.com https://da.gd; frame-src 'self' blob:; child-src blob:; worker-src 'self' blob:; font-src 'self' data:; base-uri 'none'; form-action 'none'; object-src 'none'; frame-ancestors 'self'; upgrade-insecure-requests
/legal
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; img-src 'self' data: blob: https://nano-gpt.com; media-src 'self' data: blob: https:; connect-src 'self' blob: https://nano-gpt.com; frame-src 'self' blob:; child-src blob:; worker-src 'self' blob:; font-src 'self' data:; base-uri 'none'; form-action 'none'; object-src 'none'; frame-ancestors 'self'; upgrade-insecure-requests
